::Food Day 5 [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
DAY 5 FOOD CHOICE: Yogurt vs Hot Dog.
Final choice of the game.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>Salt Sludge</span><span class="day-label">Day 5 of 5</span></div>

<div class="meters-wrap">
<div class="meter-row"><div class="meter-label">Sludge</div><div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-bar-fill sludge" @style="'width: ' + $sludge + '%'"></div></div></div>
<div class="meter-row"><div class="meter-label">Nutrients</div><div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-bar-fill nutrient" @style="'width: ' + Math.min(100, $score * 2) + '%'"></div></div></div>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p class="scene">Last day, $playerName. Last meal. Your artery has been through four days of choices with you. One more.</p>

<div class="spacer"></div>

<div class="food-row">

<<link '<span class="food-emoji">🥛</span><div class="food-name">Yogurt</div>'>>
<<set $sludge to Math.max(0, $sludge - 20)>>
<<set $score to $score + 10>>
<<set $foodChoice to "yogurt">>
<<goto "Food Result">>
<</link>>

<div class="or-divider">or</div>

<<link '<span class="food-emoji">🌭</span><div class="food-name">A hot dog</div>'>>
<<set $sludge to Math.min(100, $sludge + 25)>>
<<set $foodChoice to "hotdog">>
<<goto "Food Result">>
<</link>>

</div>

<div class="spacer"></div>

</div>
</div>

<<script>>
setTimeout(function () {
  document.querySelectorAll('.food-row a.macro-link, .food-row a.link-internal').forEach(function (a) {
    a.classList.add('food-card');
  });
}, 0);
<</script>>


::Food Result [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
RESULT OF EACH FOOD CHOICE.
Tells the player what that food did to their artery and why.
Then moves to next day or final result after Day 5.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>Salt Sludge</span><span class="day-label">Day $day of 5</span></div>

<div class="meters-wrap">
<div class="meter-row"><div class="meter-label">Sludge</div><div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-bar-fill sludge" @style="'width: ' + $sludge + '%'"></div></div></div>
<div class="meter-row"><div class="meter-label">Nutrients</div><div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-bar-fill nutrient" @style="'width: ' + Math.min(100, $score * 2) + '%'"></div></div></div>
</div>

<div class="content">

<<if $foodChoice is "banana" or $foodChoice is "spinach" or $foodChoice is "beans" or $foodChoice is "sweetpotato" or $foodChoice is "yogurt">>

<div class="result-card">
<<if $foodChoice is "banana">><span class="result-emoji">🍌</span><<elseif $foodChoice is "spinach">><span class="result-emoji">🥬</span><<elseif $foodChoice is "beans">><span class="result-emoji">🍲</span><<elseif $foodChoice is "sweetpotato">><span class="result-emoji">🍠</span><<else>><span class="result-emoji">🥛</span><</if>>
<div class="result-verdict good">Good choice</div>
<p class="result-explain"><<if $foodChoice is "banana">>That banana just delivered a flood of potassium to your kidneys. They got to work immediately, flushing out excess sodium. Your artery wall relaxed.<<elseif $foodChoice is "spinach">>Spinach is one of the most potassium-dense foods around. Your artery walls eased up. Blood is moving more freely right now.<<elseif $foodChoice is "beans">>Beans are loaded with potassium and fiber. The sludge thinned out noticeably. Your vessel just got a proper clean.<<elseif $foodChoice is "sweetpotato">>Sweet potato is the quiet champion of blood pressure foods. High potassium. Low sodium. Your artery is grateful.<<else>>Yogurt brings calcium and potassium together. Both help keep blood pressure down. Good call.<</if>></p>
<div class="result-meter-after">Sludge cleared</div>
</div>

<<else>>

<div class="result-card">
<<if $foodChoice is "soup">><span class="result-emoji">🥫</span><<elseif $foodChoice is "noodles">><span class="result-emoji">🍜</span><<elseif $foodChoice is "chips">><span class="result-emoji">🍟</span><<elseif $foodChoice is "bacon">><span class="result-emoji">🥓</span><<else>><span class="result-emoji">🌭</span><</if>>
<div class="result-verdict bad">Your artery felt that</div>
<p class="result-explain"><<if $foodChoice is "soup">>That canned soup had nearly 900 milligrams of sodium in a single serving. Almost half your daily limit in one bowl. Your artery walls tightened. Sludge started forming.<<elseif $foodChoice is "noodles">>Instant noodles pack around 1500 milligrams of sodium per packet. Your artery is working harder now than it was five minutes ago.<<elseif $foodChoice is "chips">>Potato chips are one of the sneakiest sodium sources around. A single serving can contain 200 milligrams or more. Your artery walls just got a little thicker.<<elseif $foodChoice is "bacon">>Bacon is cured in salt. That sodium hit your bloodstream fast. The sludge built up quickly.<<else>>A single hot dog contains nearly 600 milligrams of sodium. Your artery noticed immediately.<</if>></p>
<div class="result-meter-after">Sludge increased. Tomorrow is a chance to clear it.</div>
</div>

<</if>>

<<if $day lt 5>>
<<set $day to $day + 1>>
<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Day Start">ON TO DAY <<print $day>></a>
<a class="btn-secondary" data-passage="Central Hub">BACK TO CARDIOCAREQUEST</a>
<<else>>
<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Final Result">SEE YOUR FINAL ARTERY</a>
<</if>>

</div>
</div>


::Final Result [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
DENOUEMENT: End of game.
Personalized message based on final sludge level.
Score shown. Option to play again.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>Salt Sludge</span><span class="day-label">5 days done</span></div>

<div class="meters-wrap">
<div class="meter-row"><div class="meter-label">Sludge</div><div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-bar-fill sludge" @style="'width: ' + $sludge + '%'"></div></div></div>
<div class="meter-row"><div class="meter-label">Nutrients</div><div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-bar-fill nutrient" @style="'width: ' + Math.min(100, $score * 2) + '%'"></div></div></div>
</div>

<div class="content">

<div class="final-card">

<<if $sludge lt 30>>
<div class="final-headline clean">Clean artery</div>
<div class="final-stats">Sludge $sludge of 100. Nutrient points $score.</div>
<div class="final-body">
<p>Your potassium choices paid off. Blood is moving freely. Your blood pressure is lower right now than it was at the start of Day 1.</p>
<p>Five days of consistent good choices. Not dramatic. Not perfect. Just noticeably better.</p>
</div>
<<elseif $sludge lt 60>>
<div class="final-headline middle">Some sludge</div>
<div class="final-stats">Sludge $sludge of 100. Nutrient points $score.</div>
<div class="final-body">
<p>A mix of good and tough choices. Your artery is managing but working harder than it needs to.</p>
<p>The good news is you already know which foods cleared it. Those are the ones to reach for more often.</p>
</div>
<<else>>
<div class="final-headline heavy">Heavy sludge</div>
<div class="final-stats">Sludge $sludge of 100. Nutrient points $score.</div>
<div class="final-body">
<p>A tough five days. Your artery has been working overtime.</p>
<p>The sodium added up faster than the potassium could clear it. That is the most common pattern. And now you can see exactly why it matters.</p>
</div>
<</if>>

</div>

<p class="scene">Every banana, every handful of spinach, every bowl of beans is clearing sludge in real arteries right now. Including yours.</p>

<div class="spacer"></div>

<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Story innit">PLAY AGAIN</a>
<a class="btn-secondary" data-passage="Central Hub">BACK TO CARDIOCAREQUEST</a>

</div>
</div>


::Central Hub [Important/Needed nobr]
/*
Placeholder passage. In the full app this returns
the player to the CardioCareQuest main hub.
*/

<div class="phone">
<div class="header"><span>Salt Sludge</span></div>
<div class="content">

<h2 class="intro-title">Returning</h2>
<p class="narrative center">Returning to CardioCareQuest.</p>

<div class="spacer"></div>

<a class="btn-primary" data-passage="Story innit">PLAY SALT SLUDGE AGAIN</a>

</div>
</div>
